
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"> 
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin> 
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@100&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<head>
         <style>
            a {
              text-decoration: none;
            }
            section {
              display: block;
              width: 100%;
              padding: 10px;
              font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
              font-weight: 500;
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 150%;
              letter-spacing: 0.015em;
              color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            }
             .black_p {
              margin-top: 30px;
              margin-bottom: 30px;
              }
            .button {
              display: grid;
              justify-items: center;
              width: 258px;
              background-color: #4494f2;
              outline: none;
              padding-top: 7px;
              padding-bottom: 7px;
              border-radius: 30px;
              color: white;
              cursor: pointer;
              margin: 35px auto;
              display: grid;
            }
            .button > p {
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 600;
              font-style: normal;
              font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
              text-transform: uppercase;
              border: none;
              color: white;
              text-align: center;
              margin: 0;
            }
            .logoWrap {
              display: grid;
              justify-content: center;
              width: 100% ;
              color: #4494f2;
            }
            .logoWrap img {
              width: 95px;
              display: flex;
              margin: 0 auto;
            }
             .logoWrap >a >img {
              width: 95px;
              background: #fff;
              margin: 0 auto;
            }
            .content {
              display: block;
              text-align: center;
            }
            .child {
              margin-top: 30px;
              font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
              font-style: normal;
              font-weight: 500;
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 150%;
              color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
              text-align: center;
            }

        </style>
</head>
<body>
<section>
    <div class="logoWrap" style="margin: 0 auto;">
      <img src="cid:logo" alt='logo'/>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class='child'>
            Hi, {{name}}
            <br />
            <p>You recently requested to reset your password for your Test-Auth API account.</p>
            <br />
            <p>Click the button below to reset it.</p>
        </div>
        <a href={{url}} class="button">
          <p>reset your password</p>
        </a>
        <div class="child">
          <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
          <br />
          <p>This password reset is only valid for the next 30 minutes.</p>
          <p class="black_p" />
          Thanks,
          <br />
          Test-Auth API Team
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
</body>
</html>
